(177, 1, '2016-06-10 18:32:16', '2016-06-10 18:32:16', 'In this Level you’ll set-up a profile on Credly so you can earn, store, and share badges. You''ll also issue a badge to one or more people who demonstrate skills, values or behaviors you have witnessed first-hand.', 'Begin Earning & Issuing Badges', 'In this Level you’ll set-up a profile on Credly so you can earn, store, and share badges. You''ll also issue a badge to one or more people who demonstrate skills, values or behaviors you have witnesses first-hand.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'begin-earning-issuing-badges', '', '', '2016-06-10 18:32:16', '2016-06-10 18:32:16', '', 0, 'http://innovate.geniusworks.co.za/level/begin-earning-issuing-badges/', 0, 'level', '', 0),
