(188, 1, '2016-06-10 18:32:23', '2016-06-10 18:32:23', 'A badge says as much about the person or group who issued it as it does about the recipient.  To earn this "Issuer" badge, you will think about something you value in the world, define the criteria by which you and others will know that value has been exhibited, and then identify someone who deserves to be recognized.', 'Badge Issuer', 'To earn this "Issuer" badge, you will think about something you value in the world, define the criteria by which you and others will know that value has been exhibited, and then identify someone who deserves to be recognized.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'badge-issuer', '', '', '2016-06-10 18:32:23', '2016-06-10 18:32:23', '', 0, 'http://innovate.geniusworks.co.za/quest-badge/badge-issuer/', 0, 'quest-badge', '', 0),
